<section class="brand--cabinet-office brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What the Government Office for Science does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>We advise the Prime Minister and members of the Cabinet, to ensure that government policies and decisions are informed by the best scientific evidence and strategic long-term thinking.</p>

<p><abbr title="Government Office for Science">GO-Science</abbr> works with the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy">Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/government-office-for-science/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

